    "Also, it supports searches across the catalogue [Chagué and Clérice, 2022b, slide 10].",
    "From the catalogue on the HTR-United website (see 5), it is possible to download the metadata into Zotero as an 'Item Type: (Digital) Document'.",
    "This download option simplifies the future referencing process (see fig. 6).",
    "foot_7 To briefly conclude the section on sharing the data, we would like to emphasise four key approaches to processed textual data for future text recognition.",
